obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line 1
  line `THE WEALTH-TAX ACT, 1957`
  line `(Modified as on 12th November 2018)`
  line _________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line __________
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `C HARGE OF WEALTH-TAX AND ASSETS SUBJECT TO SUCH CHARGE`
  line `3. Charge of wealth-tax.`
  line `4. Net wealth to include certain assets.`
  line `5. Exemptions in respect of certain assets.`
  line `6. Exclusion of assets and debts outside India.`
  line `7. Value of assets, how to be determined.`
  line `CHAPTER III`
  line `W EALTH-TAX AUTHORITIES`
  line `8. Wealth-tax authorities and their jurisdiction.`
  line `8A. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `8AA. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `8B. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `9. Control of wealth-tax authorities.`
  line `9A. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `10. Instructions to subordinate authorities.`
  line `10A. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `11. Jurisdiction of Assessing Officers and power to transfer cases.`
  line `11A. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `11AA. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `11B. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `12. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `12A. Appointment of Valuation Officers.`
  line `13. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `13A. Powers of Director-General or Director, Chief Commissioner or Commissioner and Joint`
  line `Commissioner to make enquiries.`
  line ` Subject to verification and confirmation by the Department.`
