  line `35C. Failure to produce accounts, records, etc.`
  line `35D. False statement in verification, etc., made under certain provisions of the Act.`
  line `35E. False statement in verification mentioned in section 34AB.`
  line `35EE. Failure to furnish particulars under section 34ACC.`
  line `35EEE. Contravention of order made under second proviso to sub-section ( 1 ) or sub-section ( 3A ) of`
  line `section 37A.`
