  string
  line 9
  line `1 [Provided further that in relation to the assessment year commencing on the 1st day`
  line `of April, 1983 or any subsequent assessment year, this sub-clause shall have effect`
  line `subject to the modification that for item ( i ) thereof, the following item shall be`
  line `substituted, namely: —`
  line `( i ) ( a ) agricultural land and growing crops (including fruits on trees), grass or`
  line `standing trees on such land;`
  line `( b ) one building or one group of buildings owned or occupied by a cultivator of,`
  line `or receiver of rent or revenue out of, agricultural land:`
  line `Provided that such buildings or group of buildings is on or in the immediate`
  line `vicinity of the land and is a building which the cultivator or the receiver of rent or`
  line `revenue by reason of his connection with the land requires as store-house or for`
  line `keeping livestock;`
  line `( c ) animals:]`
  line `2 [ 3 [Provided also that]] in relation to the State of Jammu and Kashmir*, this`
  line `sub-clause shall have effect subject to the modification that for the assets specified`
  line `in 4 [item ( i )] of this sub-clause, the assets specified in 5 [items ( i ) to ( iii )] of sub-clause`
  line `( 1 ) shall be substituted and the other provisions of this Act shall be construed`
  line accordingly;]
  line `6 [( ea ) “ assets ”, in relation to the assessment year commencing on the 1st day of April, 1993, or any`
  line `subsequent assessment year, means —`
  line `7 [( i ) any building or land appurtenant thereto (hereinafter referred to as “ house ” ), whether`
  line `used for residential or commercial purposes or for the purpose of maintaining a guest house or`
  line `otherwise including a farm house situated within twenty-five kilometres from local limits of any`
  line `municipality (whether known as Municipality, Municipal Corporation or by any other name) or a`
  line `Cantonment Board, but does not include —`
  line `( 1 ) a house meant exclusively for residential purposes and which is allotted by a company`
  line `to an employee or an officer or a director who is in whole-time employment, having a gross`
  line `annual salary of less than 8 [ten lakh rupees];`
  line `( 2 ) any house for residential or commercial purposes which forms part of stock-in-trade;`
  line `( 3 ) any house which the assessee may occupy for the purposes of any business or`
  line `profession carried on by him;`
  line `( 4 ) any residential property that has been let-out for a minimum period of three hundred`
  line `days in the previous year;`
  line `( 5 ) any property in the nature of commercial establishments or complexes;]`
  line `( ii ) motor cars (other than those used by the assessee in the business of running them on hire`
  line `or as stock-in-trade);`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 33 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `2. Added by Act 19 of 1970, s. 26 (w.r.e.f. 1-4-1969)`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 33, for “Provided further that” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1983).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 20 of 1974, s. 14, for “items ( i ) to ( iii )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1975).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 14, ibid., for “items ( i ) to ( v )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1975).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 89 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 67, for sub-clause ( i ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1999). Earlier sub-clause ( i ) was substituted by Act 33 of 1996, s.`
  line `56 (w.e.f 1-4-1997).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 115, for “five lakh rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and`
  line `Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
