  title `Page 29`
  content obj_root_law_sections_29_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_29_footnotes
  sourcePage 29
obj_root_law_sections_29_content:
  string
  line 29
  line `( 1A ) No notice under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be issued for the relevant assessment year, —`
  line `1 [( a ) if four years have elapsed from the end of the relevant assessment year, unless the case falls`
  line `under clause ( b ) 2 [or clause ( c )];`
  line `( b ) if four years, but not more than six years, have elapsed from the end of the relevant`
  line `assessment year unless the net wealth chargeable to tax which has escaped assessment amounts to or`
  line `is likely to amount to rupees ten lakhs or more for that year;]`
  line `2 [( c ) if four years, but not more than sixteen years, have elapsed from the end of the relevant`
  line `assessment year unless the net wealth in relation to any asset (including financial interest in any`
  line `entity) located outside India, chargeable to tax, has escaped assessment for any assessment year.]`
  line `3 [ Explanation 1 ]. — For the purposes of sub-section ( 1 ) and sub-section ( 1A ), the following shall also`
  line `be deemed to be cases where net wealth chargeable to tax has escaped assessment, namely: —`
  line `( a ) where no return of net wealth has been furnished by the assessee although his net wealth or`
  line `the net wealth of any other person in respect of which he is assessable under this Act on the valuation`
  line `date exceeded the maximum amount which is not chargeable to wealth-tax;`
  line `( b ) where a return of net wealth has been furnished by the assessee but no assessment has been`
  line `made and it is noticed by the Assessing Officer that the assessee has understated the net wealth or has`
  line `claimed excessive exemption or deduction in the return;`
  line `2 [( c ) where a person is found to have any asset (including financial interest in any entity) located`
  line `outside India.]`
  line `2 [ Explanation 2. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby clarified that the provisions of this section,`
  line `as amended by the Finance Act, 2012, shall also be applicable for any assessment year beginning on or`
  line `before the 1st day of April, 2012 (23 of 2012).]`
  line `( 1B ) ( a ) In a case where an assessment under sub-section ( 3 ) of section 16 or sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `of this section has been made for the relevant assessment year, no notice shall be issued under`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) 4 [by an Assessing Officer, who is below the rank of 5 [Assistant Commissioner or Deputy`
  line `Commissioner], unless the 6 [Joint Commissioner] is satisfied, on the reasons recorded by such Assessing`
  line `Officer, that it is a fit case for the issue of such notice]:`
  line `Provided that, after the expiry of four years from the end of the relevant assessment year, no such`
  line `notice shall be issued unless the Chief Commissioner or Commissioner is satisfied, on the reasons`
  line `recorded by the Assessing Officer aforesaid, that it is a fit case for the issue of such notice.`
  line `( b ) In a case other than a case falling under clause ( a ), no notice shall be issued under sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `by an Assessing Officer, who is below the rank of 6 [Joint Commissioner], after the expiry of four years`
  line `from the end of the relevant assessment year, unless the 6 [Joint Commissioner] is satisfied, on the reasons`
  line `recorded by such Assessing Officer, that it is a fit case for the issue of such notice.]`
  line `7 [ Explanation. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that the Joint Commissioner, the`
  line `Commissioner or the Chief Commissioner, as the case may be, being satisfied on the reasons recorded by`
  line `the Assessing Officer about fitness of a case for the issue of notice, need not issue such notice himself.]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 96, for clauses ( a ) and ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-6-2001).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 116 (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
  line `3. The Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 thereof by s. 116, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 55, for “except by an Assessing Officer of the rank of Assistant Commissioner or Deputy`
  line `Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1990).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 66, for “Assistant Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `6. Subs. by s. 66, ibid., for “Deputy Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 60 (w.r.e.f. 1-10-1998).`
